column3: The sample file for Detection and AIS Correlation submission are available in the Data folder for reference. The files are to be submitted with same names.
The AIS Correlation is to be undertaken only on the five (05) images as indicated above in the remarks column
The Lat,Long of AIS correlation submission should be the Centre point of the detection bounding Box
The MMSI of vessels not co-related with AIS are to be marked as '0'
